sellerAgent.name: The Janice Overbeck Real Estate Team

data.description: Welcome to this stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home nestled in the desirable Legacy Pointe community, conveniently situated in a quiet cul-de-sac. Built in 2018, this modern residence boasts a perfect blend of style, functionality, and comfort. As you step through the entrance, you are greeted by beautiful hardwood floors that seamlessly flow throughout the main floor, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The spacious foyer sets the tone for the home's open and airy design. To the right of the entrance, you'll find a versatile space that can be used as a formal dining room, home office, or sitting room, offering flexibility to suit your lifestyle. The remainder of the main floor unfolds into an expansive open concept kitchen, living, and dining area. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring stained wood cabinets, stainless steel appliances, an island, breakfast bar, stone counters, and a convenient walk-in pantry. The living room, bathed in natural light from numerous windows, is adorned with a cozy fireplace, creating a perfect gathering spot for family and friends. Step through the living room's door to access the back deck, where you can enjoy outdoor living and entertaining. Completing the main level is a thoughtfully placed half bathroom for the convenience of guests. Ascend the staircase to discover a large loft area that connects all the bedrooms, providing additional living space for various activities. The primary suite is a true retreat with his and hers closets and an ensuite bathroom. The ensuite features double vanities, a separate shower, and a luxurious tub, offering a spa-like experience. Three generously sized secondary bedrooms share a full bathroom with double vanities and a shower/tub combo, providing comfort and convenience for the entire family. The upper floor also hosts the laundry room, adding practicality to your daily routine. The large unfinished basement presents an opportunity to customize and personalize the home according to your unique taste and needs. A door in the basement allows easy access to the backyard. Outside, an uncovered back deck off the main level beckons you to relax and enjoy the serene surroundings. The expansive green space provides ample room for outdoor activities, making this property a true haven. There is also an attached 2 car garage for all of  your parking and storage needs. Don't miss the chance to make this meticulously crafted home in Legacy Pointe yours – a perfect blend of elegance, comfort, and modern living.
